an Accredited Buyer\u2019s Representative (ABR) with specialized training on the unique needs of home buyers. She is also a Certified Residential Specialist (CRS) and a Graduate of the Real Estate Institute (GRI). Linda makes it a priority to focus on your goals, to explain your options and to provide excellent service in order to ensure a positive home buying or selling experience.<\/p><p>Linda is a licensed Realtor with Horizon Realty. In her free time she enjoys walking her dog, Toby, traveling and relaxing with family and friends. Linda\u2019s other hobbies include movies, music, wine-tasting and exploring small Texas towns.<\/p><p><strong>Office:<\/strong> 512.342.1800\u00a0<br \/><strong>Email:<\/strong>\u00a0<a href=\"mailto:Linda@AustinHomesByLinda.com\">Linda@AustinHomesByLinda.com<\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac11626 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"ac11626\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<style>\n.elementor-column.elementor-col-33 ul.elementor-icon-list-items {\n    padding-bottom: 10px;\n}    \n<\/style>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Management Team Linda Holmbeck Sales Director Contact Linda Holmbeck is a fourth-generation Austinite with over a decade of residential real estate experience. She holds a B.A. from the University of Texas at Austin and has been a licensed Realtor since January, 2001. Linda provides her clients with extensive knowledge of the Austin and Central Texas [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"elementor_header_footer","meta":{"_vp_format_video_url":"","_vp_image_foca